 Project Management Tool

This is a full-stack Project Management Tool with **User Login and Registration**, developed as part of the **CodeAlpha Full Stack Development Internship**.

Features

- User registration and login
- Project creation
- View all projects
- Backend authentication logic

Technologies Used

- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Backend: Node.js, Express.js
- API: REST API

Project Structure

CodeAlpha_ProjectManagement/
├── backend/
│   ├── server.js
│   ├── package.json
├── frontend/
│   ├── login.html
│   ├── dashboard.html
│   ├── style.css
│   ├── script.js

How to Run

1. Open backend folder  
   `cd backend`
2. Install dependencies  
   `npm install`
3. Start server  
   `npm start`
4. Open `frontend/login.html` in browser


